  "why_section": {
    "eyebrow": "Why Orbit Logic",
    "heading": "We Only Work With Trades — That Makes Us Better at It",
    "sub": "Most web agencies take any client that comes through the door. We deliberately don't. Our entire process, knowledge base, and design system is built around trade businesses — which means faster results and less hand-holding on your end.",
    "card_1_heading": "Deep Trades Industry Knowledge",
    "card_1_body": "We understand how trade customers search, what makes them trust a business, and what causes them to enquire. That knowledge shapes every design and content decision.",
