    "card_2_body": "A proven project process gets your site live within weeks, not months — with clear milestones, regular check-ins, and no surprises on costs.",
    "card_3_heading": "Built for Queensland's Local Market",
    "card_3_body": "We're Queensland-based and understand local search behaviour, seasonal patterns, and what trade customers in your area are actually looking for before they hire someone.",
    "card_4_heading": "Measured by Results, Not Just Looks",
    "card_4_body": "Lead volume, conversion rate, and cost-per-enquiry are the metrics that matter. We track and report on them — so you can see the return on your investment."
